cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MS, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on the development of a deep learning-based reconstruction framework for efficient MR parameter mapping, which involves image processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep learning methods, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of physical models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MS (Mathematical Software) or cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves the use of incoherent k-space sampling, which suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
